PHP Programs Collection – Semester Project


Overview
This repository contains all the PHP programs and practicals I have completed during my semester. It covers fundamental to intermediate concepts of PHP including form handling, string manipulation, file handling, sessions, and database connectivity.


Objectives

To understand core PHP syntax and structure
To implement server-side scripting concepts
To practice real-world programming problems using PHP
To build a strong foundation in web development


Technologies Used
PHP
HTML
CSS (for basic styling)
MySQL (for database-related programs)
XAMPP / WAMP (local server environment)
